# Factory Dashboard API - Sample Requests
# 
# This file contains example API requests that can be used to test the backend.
# 
# Tools to use:
# - curl (command line)
# - Postman (GUI)
# - HTTPClient plugin in VS Code
# - REST Client extension in VS Code

###
# 1. HEALTH CHECK
GET http://localhost:5000/health

###
# 2. SEED DATABASE WITH DUMMY DATA
