###
# NOTES:
# 
# - Replace http://localhost:5000 with your API server URL
# - All timestamps must be in ISO 8601 format (with Z suffix for UTC)
# - Worker IDs: W1-W6
# - Station IDs: S1-S6
# - Event types: working, idle, absent, product_count
# - Confidence: 0.0 to 1.0
# - Count: Only used for product_count events
#
# TESTING WITH CURL:
#
# curl http://localhost:5000/health
# curl http://localhost:5000/api/workers
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/seed
# 
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/events \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"timestamp":"2026-02-06T14:30:00Z","worker_id":"W1","workstation_id":"S1","event_type":"working","confidence":0.95,"count":0}'
